name: Dr. Richard Muldoone
bio: Dr. Muldoone obtained his degree in Herbal Medicine from the International University of Natural Health. He specializes in creating personalized herbal remedies for various health conditions.

name: Dr. Julia Jhones
bio: Dr. Jhones specializes in Ayurvedic treatments, addressing health issues using traditional Indian herbal practices. She is dedicated to revitalizing the appearance of skin and overall health.

name: Dr. Maria Andaloro
bio: Dr. Andaloro specializes in pediatric herbal medicine, providing natural treatments for children's health. She combines modern practices with traditional herbal remedies.

name: Dr. Kiano Barker
bio: Dr. Barker is an expert in Traditional Chinese Medicine, utilizing acupuncture and herbal formulas to treat chronic conditions and improve overall well-being.

name: Dr. Dupree Black
bio: Dr. Black diagnoses and treats health issues using natural therapies and herbal treatments. He focuses on holistic approaches to improve overall health.

name: Dr. Markus Skar
bio: Dr. Skar specializes in botanical medicine, using plant-based treatments to address a variety of health conditions. He emphasizes eco-friendly practices in his treatments.

name: Dr. John Henry
bio: Dr. Henry integrates traditional herbal practices with modern medical knowledge to provide comprehensive health solutions. He focuses on natural healing and preventative care.
office: 47 NE. Circle Dr., New York, NY 10011

name: Dr. Michael Brian
bio: Dr. Brian specializes in herbal dermatology, treating skin conditions with natural remedies. He addresses cosmetic issues and enhances the health of skin and nails.
